{"tid":907983,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實古代亞洲既匈奴同西歐既匈係咪同一個種族呢？","createTime":"2018-11-19T08:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T15:08:14.000Z","uid":101976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98b6a6b1d8a5f0611a05318e6b04dcb75ec44ee8","tid":907983,"uid":101976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"近排玩番全面戰爭阿提拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以為用緊既匈人係匈奴人勢力，但維基左先知兩個係唔同種族。兩族都擅長馬上作戰，而騎馬再加上射箭呢個組合真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家又點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa0325e6c29a74794a7d2a7cacb34c3263f674d","tid":907983,"uid":167592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"No, 完"},{"pid":"76b71b83a9884763d65b750142732d59a0f43d74","tid":907983,"uid":2267,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"亞洲嘅胸奴同西歐嘅胸都唔一樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2004eb091414c7fdd0e0774ccf0c24514e066694","tid":907983,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"冇人G 因為冇文字紀錄"},{"pid":"13561e21d3f8201e76c1bfd1b4c22bb3a3055905","tid":907983,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"其實擅長馬上作戰係自斯基泰人以來已有嘅特質，除咗Huns之外，Avar、Buglar、Turks同Magyars都係馬背作戰嘅民族。"},{"pid":"7bab3229ac89464d31208d33cd75badf8b50a95d","tid":907983,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"匈奴 = 匈牙利<br />\n突厥 = 土耳其<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef97139fa362383e2a509d235984e41fe89900a7","tid":907983,"uid"